76
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,250
Yan Lidong?

77
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,770
Yeah, what about it?

78
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,490
Must be a coincidence.

79
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,119
Hello, Mr. Fan.

80
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,850
I'm Yan Lidong, a new actor.

81
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:55,399
(What's going on?)

82
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,370
(Is the boss pretending not to know me?)

83
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,570
(Could he be trying
to experience life as a rookie?)

84
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,879
- I'll sit...
- No...

85
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:04,879
You sit. I don't need to.

86
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:05,759
I can stand.

87
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:06,999
- That's not right.
- No, no.

88
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,519
It's fine, just sit.

89
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:10,050
Our boss appreciates talent.

90
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:11,650
